{"tid":1538845,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國防部開發軟件打擊假新聞","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:13:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f930ecf4a836f9776f6bb347f2f00c1f8746bfff","tid":1538845,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190904/20761834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190904%2F20761834&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq1RUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=64a74f2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190904%2F20761834&h=a039f833\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190904/20761834</a><br />\n<br />\n美國防部開發軟件打擊假新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190904/large/1567527270_8e80.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190904%2Flarge%2F1567527270_8e80.gif&h=7f4cf214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國防部<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鑑於人工智能換臉工具「deepfake」等能製造假新聞的工具風靡全球，美國國防部正在研發一套程式，能偵測網絡資訊中過往機器難以發現、但人類能察覺到的錯誤信息，避免假新聞危害國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對換臉程式<br />\n<br />\n國防高等研究計劃署（DARPA）指，程式能偵測網絡資訊的細節部份，如演出者戴鴛鴦耳環、牙齒不尋常、頭髮凌亂和使用不正常的背景等，現已成功在50萬個報道、圖片、影片和錄音中篩選出假資料。研究人員未來四年會在程式中加入大量新聞和社交媒體內容，在當中夾雜假資訊，以建立數據庫，加強程式篩選能力。<br />\n<br />\n「deepfake」近期廣受歡迎，中國手機軟件開發商早前推出換臉軟件ZAO，隨即有數百萬人下載。過去有人以「deepfake」製造假新聞，作為攻擊政敵的工具。美國前總統奧巴馬和喬治布殊的面孔都曾被用以製作他們沒有發表過的言論，令假新聞比以往更難打擊，有機會成為干預選舉的工具。<br />\n<br />\n雪城大學通訊專家格利基爾指出，國防部以新程式打擊假新聞的確令人鼓舞，但仍存在很大漏洞，只有正式立法監察才能杜絕問題。<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n法擬以千億援助伊朗救核協議"},{"pid":"a4cd5f5824b443d40ce67c29b63115c81b8ed143","tid":1538845,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想入去打工"},{"pid":"f69aacae7fca3cadc98870ecaefa2524f4003b6c","tid":1538845,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0c457c5c71ccd6fc040a1a710421306cd223bd","tid":1538845,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4cd5f5824b443d40ce67c29b63115c81b8ed143","tid":1538845,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想入去打工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"其實又會引起另一種問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1b92e6293bad4c2ed7391b539c1d654e26995f","tid":1538845,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0c457c5c71ccd6fc040a1a710421306cd223bd","tid":1538845,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4cd5f5824b443d40ce67c29b63115c81b8ed143","tid":1538845,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想入去打工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"其實又會引起另一種問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea09c76e67f05ee68a637fc7d505c53edb63713","tid":1538845,"uid":74155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:13:15.